heading: Plucked instrument ensembles.
general-note: Here are entered compositions not in a specific form or of a specific type for ten or more different solo plucked stringed instruments and collections of compositions in several forms or types for various numbers or combinations of solo plucked stringed instruments..
When used for an accompanying ensemble in headings with medium of performance, the term "plucked instrument ensemble" stands for two or more plucked stringed instruments..
Collections of compositions for three or more solo plucked keyboard instruments are entered under. Keyboard instrument ensembles..
